Feature: CRM New Prospect Creation 
@ProspectCreationCRM
Scenario Outline: Login to CRM Application 
	Given User Launch the CRM Full Application login page 
	When the user enters valid username "<username>" and valid password "<password>" 
	And clicks the login button 
	And User should be redirected to the dashboard 
	
	
	Examples: 
		| username | password |
		| mounika.golla@advisorgroup.com.crm2.qafull | $aLesforcE123 |
@ProspectCreationCRM		
Scenario Outline: New Prospect Creation Personal Profile 
	User updates personal information
	When User select the Business Development and leads 
	And User Verifies whether the New Button is available and click 
	And User Validate the NewLead Header "New Lead: Standard" is present 
	When user enters "<FirstName>" value in FirstName field and "<LastName>" value in LastName field 
	When user enters the "<FINRA>" values in FINRACD 
	When user enters the "<DOB>" values in DOB Field 
	
	Examples: 
		| FirstName | LastName | DOB  | FINRA |
		| AutoJohn  | Doetest | 03/19/1993 | 54389 |
@ProspectCreationCRM		
Scenario Outline: New Prospect Creation Business Profile 
	User updates Business information
	When User Validate the "Business Profile" is present 
	When user enters "<BusiName>" value in Business Name(DBA) field and "<BranName>" value in Branch Name field 
	And user scroll to Assigning space 
	
	Examples: 
		| BusiName | BranName |
		| AutomationTest | TestAutomation |	
@ProspectCreationCRM		
Scenario Outline: New Prospect Creation Assign and Reviewing
	user assign Recruiters and wealth management firm
	When User validate "Assign To" is present 
	And user assign External Recruiter Name 
	And user assign Internal Recruiter Name 
	And User assign wealth management firm 
	And User enters "<Mobile>" value in personal mobile Number field and "<email>" in personal email field 
	And User selcts the recruiting lead source 
	And user selects 'Solo' from the Current Type of Practice dropdown from Contacting section 
	And user click on Save Button 
	Then User Validate the Success message Toaster 
	
	Examples: 
		| Mobile | email |
		| 555-444-3322 | TestAutomation@yahooTest.in |	
@ProspectCreationCRM		
Scenario: New Prospect Creation Convert Lead
	User Navigated to new page for convert lead
    When User validate the Header Name
    And User click on convert lead button
    And User click on convert button
    Then user validate the "Your lead has been converted" popup message
